              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Identify AI-Specific Vulnerabilities</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Learn to recognize and exploit unique security flaws in LLMs, chatbots, and AI-powered applications that traditional scanners miss.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Execute Prompt Injection Attacks</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Master advanced prompt engineering techniques to bypass AI guardrails, manipulate outputs, and extract sensitive information.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Assess ML Model Security</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Evaluate machine learning models for poisoning, adversarial attacks, and data leakage vulnerabilities using practical testing methods.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Secure AI Integrations</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Design and implement security controls for AI APIs, RAG systems, and enterprise AI deployments to prevent exploitation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Understand OWASP Top 10 for LLMs</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Deep dive into the OWASP LLM Top 10 vulnerabilities with hands-on exploitation and mitigation strategies.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Conduct AI Security Assessments</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Perform comprehensive security testing of AI systems and produce professional assessment reports with actionable recommendations.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Training Modules -->
  <section id="modules" class="py-20 px-6 bg-black">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Training Modules
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">
          Comprehensive curriculum covering the full spectrum of AI security
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <!-- Module 1 -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-950 p-8 rounded-xl border border-indigo-500/30 hover:border-indigo-500/50 transition">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl">
              01
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">AI Security Fundamentals</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
                Build foundational knowledge of how AI systems work, their architecture, and where security risks emerge. Understand LLM basics, transformer models, and AI deployment patterns.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600/20 text-indigo-300 text-sm rounded-full">LLM Architecture</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600/20 text-indigo-300 text-sm rounded-full">AI/ML Basics</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600/20 text-indigo-300 text-sm rounded-full">Deployment Models</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600/20 text-indigo-300 text-sm rounded-full">Threat Modeling</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Module 2 -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-950 p-8 rounded-xl border border-indigo-500/30 hover:border-indigo-500/50 transition">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl">
              02
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Prompt Injection & Manipulation</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
                Master the art of prompt injection attacks. Learn direct and indirect injection techniques, jailbreaking methods, and how to bypass content filters and safety mechanisms.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600/20 text-indigo-300 text-sm rounded-full">Direct Injection</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600/20 text-indigo-300 text-sm rounded-full">Indirect Injection</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600/20 text-indigo-300 text-sm rounded-full">Jailbreaking</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600/20 text-indigo-300 text-sm rounded-full">Filter Bypass</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Module 3 -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-950 p-8 rounded-xl border border-indigo-500/30 hover:border-indigo-500/50 transition">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl">
              03
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Data Leakage & Privacy Attacks</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
                Discover how sensitive information leaks through AI systems. Extract training data, exploit memory vulnerabilities, and understand privacy risks in LLM deployments.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600/20 text-indigo-300 text-sm rounded-full">Training Data Extraction</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600/20 text-indigo-300 text-sm rounded-full">PII Leakage</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600/20 text-indigo-300 text-sm rounded-full">Context Poisoning</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600/20 text-indigo-300 text-sm rounded-full">Memory Attacks</span>
