                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600/20 text-indigo-300 text-sm rounded-full">Data Poisoning</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600/20 text-indigo-300 text-sm rounded-full">Adversarial Examples</span>
